ADO-EKITI- The management of the Ekiti State Sports Council has hinted that the recently signed Ekiti State  Sports Development Trust Fund(SDTF) would boast the morale of the athletes. The General Manager, Ekiti State Sports Council, Mr. Deji Samo, who applauded the governor Kayode Fayemi for the feat, said it would  make sector more reliable and  enhance the capacity of  youths sporting activities Samo added that Fayemi has made giant strides to develop the sector  by ways of creating the ministry of Sports, regrassing of Oluyemi Kayode Stadium and the sponsorship of the Ekiti United Football Club and a female team for the state. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! He thanked the State House of Assembly for the speedy passage of the bill, he described as potent weapon that would bolster sports sector in the state. The GM in a statement on weekend quoted Fayemi as saying  that the fund would bring more development to the sports when implemented . CAF League: Al Mereikh Promise $250,000 Reward To Beat Enyimba Japan Reiterates Promise To Hold Olympics Fayemi said with the fund in place, there would be Public-Private partnership in the sponsorship of sporting activities and make the sector a priority of government in terms of funding . “SDTF is strategic for the development of sports. Now that white collar jobs are not in place, there would be need for us to develop the sports sector to help in generating employments for our youths and build their skills to be able to compete locally, nationally and internationally”. Said the GM  “The board and the management of sports appreciate the SDTF that was signed into law by Governor Fayemi. This is unprecedented and will boost sporting activities in our dear state. “With this , our athletes  can now attain a higher height and win more laurels and trophies for our dear state locally, nationally and internationally. “Sport is a money spinning activity, but capital intensive. Now that more  funding will be available through SDTF, Ekiti will soon gain recognition as a state where huge potentials abound in sports and we can rake in more revenues into the State” . SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION